{"tid":1547011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[外國文宣] 眾籌網上賣廣告有人會課金嗎?","createTime":"2019-09-06T13:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T13:53:58.000Z","uid":273265,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"63f0f8520384a43022dd58c14de6beb5f3fb6140","tid":1547011,"uid":273265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:51:51.000Z","msg":"大家都知Stand with Hong Kong at G20嘅廣告揚威海外<br />\n但其實比起報紙廣告,網上廣告更有用呀!<br />\n例如 Brexit 同 cambridge analytica, 我諗大家唔會陌生,網上廣告能力比紙媒高<strong>好多</strong><br />\n<br />\n於是整左個網, <a href=\"http://helphk.info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhelphk.info&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2kBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=d873aa8e\" target=\"_blank\">helphk.info</a><br />\n<strong><ins>理念:</ins></strong><br />\n話比<ins>全世界</ins>知香港發生咩事<br />\n然後產生同情,從而支持<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>點解要咁做?</ins></strong><br />\n其實我想講,好多外國人係知香港而家有D亂,句號<br />\n好多人唔知因乜事<br />\n好多人唔知犬隻橫行<br />\n情況就好似一兩個月前南蘇丹內戰咁<br />\n你知有內戰,你覺得有D慘,但你冇做任何嘢<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>有乜目標</ins></strong><br />\n開放討論<br />\n但我諗法係,用個網等多D人知道咩事,從而產生同情心<br />\n簡單D講,我想做一次cambridge analytica咁嘅嘢<br />\n而最後佢地可以做乜,有提供出路 <a href=\"http://helphk.info/helpus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhelphk.info%2Fhelpus&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2kBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=4a67ca34\" target=\"_blank\">helphk.info/helpus</a><br />\n簡單如用 Kongish <a href=\"http://helphk.info/kongish\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhelphk.info%2Fkongish&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2kBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=888522f9\" target=\"_blank\">helphk.info/kongish</a> 去 social media 出個 post<br />\n但主要係聚全球民意支持, 或者係用下廣東話去支持大家<br />\n等大家有動力堅持落去<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>問答部</ins></strong><br />\n問: 點解唔同Stand with Hong Kong一齊做?<br />\n答: 一嚟我聯絡唔到, 二嚟我方向係賣慘, 兄弟爬山<br />\n<br />\n問: 個網有好多犬暴都冇<br />\n答: 我知, 但要從讀者角度出發, 我選擇咗一部份, 最煽情嘅出嚟, 因為如果乜都放晒出, 唔會有人睇<br />\n<br />\n問: 多國語言?<br />\n答: 求協助, 但有一點想講, 我有計劃出簡中版反攻, 但內容會唔同, 所以需時<br />\n<br />\n問: 點賣廣告法?<br />\n答: 其實暫時試左一萬蚊,Google Ads 同 Facebook, Facebook 就正如cambridge analytica咁,可以好針對一D群體去做 (如左膠), 所以如果有眾籌,會主力FB,其次Google (7:3 / 8:2)<br />\n<br />\n問: 我冇錢<br />\n答: 其實暫時睇試驗, 每下點擊需要$7-10, 所以如果你唔會課金, 你將網分享比一個外國人, 就等於出左 $7-10蚊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後, 如果你睇到呢個位,多謝你<br />\n暫時未有課金渠道,想睇下有幾多正負皮再行動"},{"pid":"1f5fa9307e13dc6e0b75545894081a2a419f09ef","tid":1547011,"uid":290761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8vAmVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8vAmVU.jpg&h=305434b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門區校友街坊們過黎幫手啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f064dee3ade36c0d8e48d867ce6b81a1740a5af7","tid":1547011,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:52:44.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99468a53133456a2fa93542da7e9045d3df237bf","tid":1547011,"uid":311956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:39:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af7f00da2c93d15558c57cf3c22c2edf0fe157a1","tid":1547011,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"全港連儂牆要人，文宣要人！<br />\n<br />\n8/9 美領事館<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衛城長久戰，全民都抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；<br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests #Chinazi<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2kBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=5fbdfac1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.07"},{"pid":"9aceb1f3a3b08c01aae43d93489c262a731e1ead","tid":1547011,"uid":140000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539332cddb4f65967f6f4540bf464c894db15b27","tid":1547011,"uid":19294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:27:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b9040fdfafaf9a799421efcfeb3566d63126c4b","tid":1547011,"uid":264369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:35:02.000Z","msg":"建議為區選選區，尤其反自動當選的，各區獨立設一個台<br />\n原因：<br />\n1. 既然冇大台提供可靠懶人包結論，就要期望唔少唔多喜歡睇文字的手足認真閱讀分析 &quot;raw material&quot; ．每台只處理跟各人相關的資料，可以方便大家作出明智決定，亦方便 admin 管理（移動錯台post／垃圾文 etc）<br />\n2. 這兩天有關 歐頌賢 及 任嘉兒 的討論，大家要跟post都已經有Ｄ難度，遲下區多人多時間逼，再加大大班臥底時，肯定亂到九彩，早日作好安排好Ｄ．"},{"pid":"f4bb2f5479206636893edfb70b60384925c6a813","tid":1547011,"uid":84982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:53:26.000Z","msg":"課"},{"pid":"2053d3a18af686d59ffb7deb701010b6c29d3ce6","tid":1547011,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b0022247f4972be683aed6f3a6762c87c1ec8a","tid":1547011,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:14:40.000Z","msg":"簡中版反攻呢招唔錯"},{"pid":"719a19ca486bdd168129facd5d24cf16f0da7d10","tid":1547011,"uid":241310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:32:08.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"fe35e619afe14fb032c8aa1838cef6b7c7df95d5","tid":1547011,"uid":273265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:42:49.000Z","msg":"多謝大家支持<br />\n反應唔算熱烈,但籌備中<br />\n會盡快推出"},{"pid":"66c5e70e1ed48f417ca01edc5316d7dac418fc60","tid":1547011,"uid":273265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:53:58.000Z","msg":"[外地文宣] 認同課金買online Ads請進<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1591272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1591272</a>"}]}